  <lyrics>[V1]
 Cristo yawarninwan rantiwan.
 Cieloman kusiywan risaj.
 Khuyaynimpi kacharichiwan,
 Wawanña kani, yachani.
 
[C]
 Señor, Jesús ..........
 Yawarninwan rantiwan, Pay,
 Señor, Jesús ..........
 Paywan cieloman ripusaj.
 
[V2]
 Juchaymanta kacharichiwan,
 Kusisqalla kawsakuni.
 Almaytapis Paylla khuyaykun,
 Jesuswan may sumaj kawsay.
 
[V3]
 Cristopipuni yuyayneyqa
 Mana jayk’aj qonqaymanchu.
 Munakuyninmanta parlasaj,
 Jesusllata yupaychasaj.
 
[V4]
 Pillutaqa Paylla qowanqa,
 Allín, kawsajkunamampis.
 Salvadorwan Janaj Pachapi
 Almayqa kusikamonqa.
 
</lyrics></song>